review_data: Reviewed in the United States on February 17, 2021
name: Just Passing Through
title: Winner!
review: This has become my go-to yogurt.I like the flavor (delicious plain, a hint of an acidic tone) and texture (thick, smooth, and creamy) and have never gotten an "off" batch.I will say that whole milk yogurt is a bit of a splurge in terms of calories, but it's so worth it.In my opinion, sometimes the WF/365 brands leave something to be desired, especially in terms of flavor, but not in this case.This is a winner.

title: Good quality with quite a sharp taste.
review: I like unflavored yogurt, while my wife is not a fan.This is an appropriate thickness for a Greek style yogurt with quite a tart flavor.It tastes fresh and much like the yogurt I make at home.

title: This is really great Greek yogurt
review: I don't write reviews of grocery products. But this is really great yogurt. I eat it with granola and also use it as a sour cream substitute. Very smooth consistency. Not as tangy as sour cream but thick like sour cream.

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on August 10, 2020
name: A Customer
title: 365 Everyday Value, Organic Greek Whole Milk Yogurt is the best I've tried!
review: I will not purchase any other Organic Greek Whole Milk Yogurt now that I've tried 365 Everyday Value, Organic Greek Whole Milk Yogurt.I started off using Costco Organic Non-Fat Greek yogurt, which I loved but after purchasing 365 Everyday Value, Organic Greek Whole Milk Yogurt from Whole Foods Market delivery, I simply couldn't go back.I even tried Chobani Whole Milk Greek Yogurt but it was nothing compared to the creaminess of 365 Everyday Value, Organic Greek Whole Milk Yogurt.It's thick, creamy, and very satisfying.Thanks and Cheers to 365 and Whole Foods Delivery!
